community working here.

149
00:13:33.656 --> 00:13:36.471
What community? Jews can
no longer own businesses.

150
00:13:36.492 --> 00:13:38.300
That's why this one's
in receivership.

151
00:13:38.301 --> 00:13:39.536
But they wouldn't own it.

152
00:13:39.557 --> 00:13:42.790
I'd own it. I'd pay them back
in product-pots and pans.

153
00:13:42.915 --> 00:13:45.959
- Pots and pans.
- Something they can use.

154
00:13:46.043 --> 00:13:47.628
Something they can
feel in their hands.

155
00:13:47.711 --> 00:13:49.922
They can trade it on the black
market, do whatever they want.

156
00:13:49.943 --> 00:13:52.633
Everybody's happy.

157
00:13:53.801 --> 00:13:57.137
If you want, you could
run the company for me.

158
00:14:01.100 --> 00:14:03.227
Let me understand.

159
00:14:03.519 --> 00:14:05.959
They'd put up all the
money, I'd do all the work.

160
