anything on the street.

200
00:16:51.603 --> 00:16:55.316
We don't do that.
We're here to pray.

201
00:17:00.279 --> 00:17:02.948
Do you have any idea how much
a shirt like this costs?

202
00:17:02.985 --> 00:17:05.868
Nice things cost money.

203
00:17:18.380 --> 00:17:20.361
How many?

204
00:17:21.529 --> 00:17:24.762
I'm going to need some other
things, too, as things come up.

205
00:17:24.887 --> 00:17:28.557
